Monopoly Star Wars is the 1997 Monopoly franchise Star Wars video game based on the board game and set in the Star Wars fictional universe. It is one of many "Monopoly" video game adaptions. The game was developed by Artech Studios and published by Hasbro Interactive. It was released exclusively for Microsoft Windows computers. The game employs the same basic ruleset of traditional Monopoly gameplay, but the "Star Wars" theme includes famous characters and locales in place of the original game pieces and properties. <S> [["Monopoly Star Wars", "instance of", "Video game"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "based on", "Monopoly franchise Star Wars"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "set in", "Star Wars fictional universe"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "developed by", "Artech Studios"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "published by", "Hasbro Interactive"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "released for", "Microsoft Windows computers"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "ruleset", "traditional Monopoly gameplay"], ["Monopoly Star Wars", "theme includes", "famous characters and locales"]]
