Ala Ela is a 2014 Telugu film directed bv Aneesh Krishna and produced by Ashok Vardhan. The film stars Rahul Ravindran, Hebah Patel, Kushi, Bhanu Sri Mehra, Vennela Kishore, and Shani Salmon. The music was composed by Bheems Ceciroleo with cinematography by Sai Sri Ram. The film released on 28 November 2014. <S> [["Ala Ela", "instance of", "Telugu film"], ["Ala Ela", "director", "Aneesh Krishna"], ["Ala Ela", "producer", "Ashok Vardhan"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Rahul Ravindran"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Hebah Patel"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Kushi"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Bhanu Sri Mehra"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Vennela Kishore"], ["Ala Ela", "cast", "Shani Salmon"], ["Ala Ela", "music composer", "Bheems Ceciroleo"], ["Ala Ela", "cinematography by", "Sai Sri Ram"], ["Ala Ela", "release date", "28 November 2014"]]
